{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"1001","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"國際能源總署：今年電力需求成長快於再生能源","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>時間：2021-07-16 07:52新聞引據：中央社 撰稿編輯：新聞編輯</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><img alt='國際能源總署：今年電力需求成長快於再生能源' src='https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2020/06/03/21beab05d0e6944b2eb6747c168fa246.jpg' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;' /></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>國際能源總署(International Energy Agency, IEA) (美聯社/達志影像)</span></span></p>\n\n<hr style='box-sizing: content-box; border-radius: 0px; height: 1px; margin: 20px 0px; border-top-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(left, transparent, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), transparent); color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;' />\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>國際能源總署（IEA）15日示警，電力需求成長快於再生能源產出，導致造成嚴重空氣污染的煤炭使用激增，破壞達到碳中和的努力。</span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>因為各國祭出防止COVID-19（2019冠狀病毒疾病）疫情擴散的限制措施，全球經濟陷入衰退，今年電力需求預期將成長5%，去年則是減少1%。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>國際能源總署在每半年發布一次的電力市場報告中表示：「再生能源發電持續強勁增長，但跟不上需求增加的速度。」&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>2020年再生能源發電增加7%，國際能源總署預期今年再生能源發電將成長8%，明年則成長逾6%。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;; text-align: justify;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>國際能源總署說：「儘管產能快速增加，但預期2021和2022年再生能源只能滿足這兩年全球電力需求預期增長的一半左右。」&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'>這將讓化石燃料發電滿足今年45%的新增需求。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei !important&quot;;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; font-size: 16px;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px;'>資料來源：</span><a href='https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2105590' style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 158, 184); text-decoration-line: none; outline: 0px !important;'><span style='box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2105590</span></a></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2021-07-16","clk_count":"151"}},"__N_SSG":true}